headline: J.B. Hunt Participates in Wreaths Across America for 11th Consecutive Year
summary: LOWELL, Ark., December 09, 2024--J.B. Hunt Transport Services Inc. (NASDAQ: JBHT), one of the largest supply chain solutions providers in North America, announced today its continued participation in Wreaths Across America for the 11th consecutive year. The nationwide effort ensures fallen veterans are remembered during the holiday season.

thumbnail.caption: To commemorate its 11th year of participating in Wreaths Across America, J.B. Hunt designed a custom wrap for select tractors and trailers featuring the theme, “Your Courage Inspires Us.” (Photo: Business Wire)
